title: Nighttime sighting of two upright creatures by a motorist outside Middleburg
observed: I was driving home from work one night, down CR220 (Middleburg) turned left on SR21 (Blanding Blvd) and when I rounded the corner, my headlights caught sight of 2, not human or animals, standing by the speed limit sign and when they heard my vehicle/seen the headlights- they stopped (looked like they were rustling w/ something) and looked up.
location_details: once you turn off of cr220 and left onto blanding, the first side road to the right.
